# QR Features Now Live

## Status: LIVE

QR code features are now live and ready for use.

## Features Available

1. Enable/disable QR codes on KB articles
2. Download QR codes as PNG or SVG
3. Location metadata for physical placement
4. Public KB viewer for scanning
5. Analytics tracking

## Usage

1. Go to Knowledge Base
2. Select an article
3. Click "Enable QR"
4. Download and print
5. Post in physical location
